thread.title: Keith

author: Keith
title: Keith
text: Part arrived well packaged and on time. There was a small plastic piece that needed to be removed for my application that didn't jump out to me at first. It didn't become apparent until I mounted the lense assembly and noticed it was sticking out too far. Had I taken some time to compare the new unit to the old before I installed it I probably would have caught it. Minor set back and my fault. My first experience with the PartsGeek but I would definitely use them again.
